snippet.title: Minecraft x Disney Worlds of Adventure DLC
snippet.description:
The magical world of Disney is returning to Minecraft! 
https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=46913ebe-392d-454a-8b26-78d513e8bd1d 

In this six-part adventure by Cyclone, you’ll hunt down gem shards hidden in the iconic stories of Disney’s Aladdin, The Little Mermaid, The Lion King, Snow White, Alice in Wonderland, and Beauty & the Beast. Let the nostalgia wash over you as you roam, soar, or dive through the oh-so-familiar locations, team up with some of your favorite Disney characters, and discover new twists, mobs, and puzzles to solve.

Read more about Disney Worlds of Adventure: https://minecraft.net/article/disney-worlds-adventure]

Get the DLC now:
https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=46913ebe-392d-454a-8b26-78d513e8bd1d
